pageProduct.name: Thompson's Ultra Strength Resveratrol 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's Ultra Strength Resveratrol support cardiovascular system health and is a source of antioxidant.

Thompson's Ultra Strength Resveratrol contains a blend of Resveratrol, Vitamin C and Citrus Bioflavonoids: supports cardiovascular system health and function, supports blood vessel health, reduces free radicals formed in the body and decreases their damage to bloody cells, relievs inflammation. Suppots general health and wellbeing.

Size: 60tabs

Oil-Free?: Yes

Shelf Life in Days: 1095

KEY FEATURES

• Help provide a supplementary source of antioxidants.
• Help reduce free radical damage to body cells.
• Supports blood vessel health.
• Supports heart health.
• Supports general health & wellbeing in adults.
• Has anti-inflammatory properties to relieve inflammation.

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each tablet contains:
Reynoutria japonica (Giant Knotweed) ext. 250mg
derived from dry root 25g (25000mg)
std. to contain Resveratrol 125mg
Ascorbic acid (vitamin C) 60mg
Citrus Bioflavonoids Ext. 30mg

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken. Keep out of reach of children.

Storage Temperature: below 30°C

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Remove cap, recycle glass bottle.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
